{
  "stem": "2966.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took us to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember how many hundreds of us we were, maybe 500 people in one big room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to sit one squashed into another because there was no room to stand up or to lie down.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if anybody had to go to the bathroom, it was just-- he had to step over everybody to get out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He could never get back in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next day, they issued some kind of clothes to us, and they started practicing marching and standing at attention and taking your hats off.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And if you had a row of 200 people, and if one head went a fraction of a second not at the same time as everybody else, it was hell to pay.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They could put us kneeling down-- not kneeling down, but squatting, for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if you fell, they beat you to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- what they were doing to us was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At that time, some people from Camp Plaszow were under Schindler's list.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were all taken to Gross-Rosen with us together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But there they were separated and taken away by Schindler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I, unfortunately, didn't have that luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My friend Igor was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was on Schindler's list.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They stayed in one camp, and they survived the war there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I, on the other hand, even at Gross-Rosen, I stayed there a few days longer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we had to carry rocks, run with a rock up the hill and down the hill, up the hill and down the hill.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was no end to their cruelty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was no end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we received some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How much, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
